    "It is also a key to understanding different cultures, viewpoints, and values. \"",
    "Their experience of English's omnipresence in their academic and personal life underscores its global influence.",
    "Their immersion in English, both in academic settings and through media consumption, illustrates how English serves as a vital tool for navigating a global interconnected world.",
    "This widespread influence of English in various aspects of life reinforces its perceived importance among the participants, driving their motivation to learn and master the language.",
